{"tid":585122,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我就嚟放低到個女仔啦！！","createTime":"2018-03-08T11:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T16:01:32.000Z","uid":169676,"like":33,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"62b0bad80d0c974e7ba843c6bdca2c788861cd8a","tid":585122,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"個秘訣就係 自卑<br />\n<br />\n得個靚仔樣有撚柒用咩？？？！<br />\n無錢<br />\n無車<br />\n無樓<br />\n乜撚都無<br />\n學乜撚嘢人溝女？<br />\n<br />\n畀我溝到<br />\n出年就講分手啦<br />\n<br />\n我追條女接佢收工<br />\n接佢一齊去過聖誕夜<br />\n佢唔出聲屌鳩我<br />\n係當可憐我呢條廢柴渣<br />\n<br />\n事實係<br />\n人地條仔優秀過自己呀<br />\n醒少少啦契弟！<br />\n追追追<br />\n追你老鼠臭西呀！<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦死廢柴！<br />\n咁撚大個人仲未識醒<br />\n日日係到發春夢<br />\n折磨自己<br />\n死撚咗去啦不如！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5e245c34942b3e1a5cf6345721abf10facd296","tid":585122,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"8d07a234f35cc9320488693141776c3591420375","tid":585122,"uid":169676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"我會喪追個女仔<br />\n就係因為我太過自信<br />\n<br />\n但事實我只係一條廢柴！"},{"pid":"39ae390452b934c4816e8f1537274ab7aab59da5","tid":585122,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會喪追個女仔<br />\n就係因為我太過自信<br />\n<br />\n但事實我只係一條廢柴！</blockquote><br />\n你係廢柴 食塞米 扮晒蟹既屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"97e3226f6283a831c656e29e6dc660d8bc1a7e5c","tid":585122,"uid":169676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39ae390452b934c4816e8f1537274ab7aab59da5","tid":585122,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會喪追個女仔<br />\n就係因為我太過自信<br />\n<br />\n但事實我只係一條廢柴！</blockquote><br />\n你係廢柴 食塞米 扮晒蟹既屎忽鬼"